```py
from distutils.core import setup
from distutils.extension import Extension
setup(name='foobar',
      version='1.0',
      ext_modules=[
          Extension('foopkg.foo', ['foo.c']),
          Extension('barpkg.bar', ['bar.c']),
          ],
      )
